{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-strapi-localized","description":"Gatsby source plugin for building websites using Strapi as a data source","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","gatsby-source-plugin","localization","strapi"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"igorko82","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/ca751ea56a2feec9fb045b71d04f500a"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/ikhudo/gatsby-source-strapi-localized"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-strapi-localized\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-strapi-localized\" aria-label=\"gatsby source strapi localized permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-strapi-localized</h1>\n<p>Source plugin for pulling documents into Gatsby 2 from a Strapi API.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-source-strapi-localized</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-source-strapi`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      apiURL<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`http://localhost:1337`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      contentTypes<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`article`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`user`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      availableLngs<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'en'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'de'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token comment\">// Possibility to login with a strapi user, when content types are not publically available (optional).</span>\n      loginData<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        identifier<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        password<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"strapi-content\"><a href=\"#strapi-content\" aria-label=\"strapi content permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Strapi content</h2>\n<p>You need create fields like <code class=\"language-text\">title__en</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">title__de</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-query\"><a href=\"#how-to-query\" aria-label=\"how to query permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to query</h2>\n<p>You can query Document nodes created from your Strapi API like the following:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\"><pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allStrapiArticles <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        id\n        locales <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          title\n          content\n          lng\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>and the response will be like:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">...\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Strapi__Articles__5bb61765593d462a14cabeb4\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"locales\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"title\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"...\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"content\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"...\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"lng\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"en\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"title\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"...\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"content\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"...\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"lng\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"de\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n...</code></pre></div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-strapi-localized/","id":"7015c421-41c1-5340-a3d7-dfb9531b8e01","layout":"plugins"}}